<font color="#FFFFFF">you got me killed.</font>

186
00:09:10,015 --> 00:09:11,688
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now, you listen to me, young man.</font>

187
00:09:11,850 --> 00:09:14,355
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've punched about a thousand hearts
in my life.</font>

188
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:18,317
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I never, never missed.
- You ever been a 3-foot tall half ling...</font>

189
00:09:18,482 --> 00:09:22,159
<font color="#FFFFFF">running through 2-foot high vines
trying to punch a 7-foot monster?</font>

190
00:09:22,695 --> 00:09:24,996
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm gonna check the others.
Check your character.</font>

191
00:09:25,155 --> 00:09:28,205
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or just kind of generally take this game
seriously. Your son does.</font>

192
00:09:29,869 --> 00:09:34,460
<font color="#FFFFFF">I take a moment of silence
to mourn my fallen comrade, Crouton...</font>

193
00:09:34,624 --> 00:09:37,721
<font color="#FFFFFF">before rifling through her belongings.</font>

194
00:09:40,629 --> 00:09:43,179
<font color="#FFFFFF">- My father?
- No way to know where the others are.</font>

195
00:09:43,341 --> 00:09:45,927
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're still travelling north
along narrow cliff edges...</font>

196
00:09:46,094 --> 00:09:48,477
<font color="#FFFFFF">of Hawthorne Mountains.
I'll roll for encounters.</font>

197
00:09:48,638 --> 00:09:51,187
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'd like to cast a healing spell
on Fibrosis.</font>

198
00:09:52,057 --> 00:09:53,231
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

199
00:09:53,393 --> 00:09:56,405
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I'm not gonna help you
kick your dad out of your life.</font>

200
00:09:56,562 --> 00:09:58,567
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't think
this competition is healthy.</font>

201
00:09:58,730 --> 00:10:00,985
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't think what you did back there
was cool.</font>

202
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:04,912
<font color="#FFFFFF">You think I'm the bad guy because
I didn't invite him to my son's birthday.</font>

203
00:10:05,071 --> 00:10:06,577
<font color="#FFFFFF">But you know where he was...</font>

204
00:10:06,739 --> 00:10:08,578
<font color="#FFFFFF">for most of my birthdays?</font>

205
00:10:08,740 --> 00:10:11,706
<font color="#FFFFFF">Little place that rhymes
with "not there."</font>

206
00:10:11,870 --> 00:10:13,708
<font color="#FFFFFF">Times Square?</font>

207
00:10:14,873 --> 00:10:16,462
<font color="#FFFFFF">You hear an ominous screeching.</font>

208
00:10:16,624 --> 00:10:21,548
<font color="#FFFFFF">Moving upward into view, three huge,
white arachnids with eagle wings.</font>

209
00:10:21,712 --> 00:10:22,886
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sky Spiders.</font>

210
00:10:24,090 --> 00:10:28,432
<font color="#FFFFFF">I draw my sword, and I cry out,
"Back, eight-legged demons!</font>

211
00:10:28,595 --> 00:10:32,770
<font color="#FFFFFF">I will not scoop you up with a catalogue
and let you outside on this day!"</font>

212
00:10:32,932 --> 00:10:35,269
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stay your blade, Joseph Gordon.</font>

213
00:10:35,434 --> 00:10:38,532
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sky Spiders are as frightened of us
as we are of them.</font>

214
00:10:38,687 --> 00:10:40,443
<font color="#FFFFFF">Plus, they eat all the sky mosquitoes.</font>

215
00:10:40,606 --> 00:10:43,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">I cast "Speak with Monsters,"
and I say:</font>

216
00:10:44,818 --> 00:10:47,868
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Hello. You're looking well."</font>

217
00:10:49,157 --> 00:10:52,371
<font color="#FFFFFF">The lead spider bends four knees
and twitches its hairy ovipositor...</font>

218
00:10:52,534 --> 00:10:55,631
<font color="#FFFFFF">rhythmically secreting
and retracting a giant droplet...</font>

219
00:10:55,788 --> 00:10:57,294
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or drop... of silk.</font>

220
00:10:57,664 --> 00:10:58,957
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fibrosis, as a ranger...</font>

221
00:10:59,125 --> 00:11:01,806
<font color="#FFFFFF">you recognise this as the arachnid
signal of submission.</font>

222
00:11:02,629 --> 00:11:03,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nice work, Tristram.</font>

223
00:11:03,879 --> 00:11:07,260
<font color="#FFFFFF">Damn, you made that Sky Spider
your bitch, yo!</font>

224
00:11:10,385 --> 00:11:12,392
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've tracked the hobgoblins
to this shack.</font>

225
00:11:12,554 --> 00:11:14,809
<font color="#FFFFFF">One guard hob-guards.
What they call guarding.</font>

226
00:11:14,974 --> 00:11:16,563
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Go.
- Sniper arrow on the guard.</font>

227
00:11:16,725 --> 00:11:17,984
<font color="#FFFFFF">Strikes true. Guard drops.</font>

228
00:11:18,144 --> 00:11:21,110
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I move to the doorway, detect traps.
- None detected.</font>

229
00:11:21,272 --> 00:11:22,482
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I enter.
- Left flank.</font>

230
00:11:22,649 --> 00:11:23,990
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Right!
- One, facing east.</font>

231
00:11:24,149 --> 00:11:25,490
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Backstab.
- Double damage.</font>

232
00:11:25,652 --> 00:11:28,154
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's dead.
Footsteps behind the door to the north.</font>

233
00:11:28,321 --> 00:11:29,578
<font color="#FFFFFF">I notch two arrows.</font>

234
00:11:29,739 --> 00:11:32,953
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Climb the walls, get above the door.
- Goblins enter from the north.</font>

235
00:11:33,116 --> 00:11:34,409
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I fire.
- Both arrows hit.</font>

236
00:11:34,576 --> 00:11:36,499
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Cleave!
- You kill one and wound another.</font>

237
00:11:36,663 --> 00:11:38,466
<font color="#FFFFFF">I drop on the last one and grapple.</font>

238
00:11:38,623 --> 00:11:40,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You got a hold of him.
- This one is for Crouton.</font>

239
00:11:41,042 --> 00:11:42,596
<font color="#FFFFFF">With his dying breath, he utters:</font>

240
00:11:42,751 --> 00:11:46,761
<font color="#FFFFFF">"The dark lord will kill you all."</font>

241
00:11:46,923 --> 00:11:48,559
<font color="#FFFFFF">Wait, these things can talk?</font>

242
00:11:48,716 --> 00:11:50,222
<font color="#FFFFFF">I want two taken alive.</font>

243
00:11:50,384 --> 00:11:51,595
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wanna try something.</font>

244
00:11:51,760 --> 00:11:53,101
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hi.</font>

245
00:11:54,013 --> 00:11:55,485
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm Tiny Nuggins.</font>

246
00:11:55,639 --> 00:11:59,649
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm gonna put my dagger down
right here, so we can just talk.</font>

247
00:11:59,811 --> 00:12:00,937
<font color="#FFFFFF">Human trash.</font>

248
00:12:01,104 --> 00:12:03,606
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah, look,
I'm gonna give it to you straight.</font>

249
00:12:03,773 --> 00:12:05,244
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're looking for a necromancer.</font>

250
00:12:05,399 --> 00:12:07,321
<font color="#FFFFFF">We don't need two goblins to find him.</font>

251
00:12:07,485 --> 00:12:11,542
<font color="#FFFFFF">So between you and your friend,
who do you think's the most useful?</font>

252
00:12:12,532 --> 00:12:14,537
<font color="#FFFFFF">Man, your friend sure can talk.</font>

253
00:12:14,701 --> 00:12:16,373
<font color="#FFFFFF">Liar. He'll never turn.</font>

254
00:12:16,536 --> 00:12:18,921
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, yeah,
because of that famous goblin loyalty.</font>

255
00:12:19,080 --> 00:12:22,426
<font color="#FFFFFF">I could never drive a wedge
between you and some guy from work.</font>

256
00:12:22,583 --> 00:12:25,965
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was best man at that guy's wedding.</font>

257
00:12:26,379 --> 00:12:28,384
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your friend says you just got married.</font>

258
00:12:28,548 --> 00:12:30,719
<font color="#FFFFFF">Congratulations.
Too bad about the food.</font>

259
00:12:30,884 --> 00:12:33,470
<font color="#FFFFFF">I hope your flesh rots in... Wait.</font>

260
00:12:33,635 --> 00:12:34,809
<font color="#FFFFFF">What about the food?</font>

261
00:12:34,971 --> 00:12:37,272
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, I guess he didn't like
your wedding toast.</font>

262
00:12:37,432 --> 00:12:38,820
<font color="#FFFFFF">Golbak said that?</font>

263
00:12:38,975 --> 00:12:41,360
<font color="#FFFFFF">Klang doesn't approve of you and Lisa,
Golbak...</font>

264
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:45,695
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I don't get the sense
