265
00:12:45,856 --> 00:12:49,783
<font color="#FFFFFF">I think about Lisa, sitting in that hole
in Darktooth Canyon...</font>

266
00:12:49,943 --> 00:12:54,415
<font color="#FFFFFF">with that little Frimrok and Grignog
rolling about on the wolf pelts.</font>

267
00:12:54,573 --> 00:12:57,538
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on, between you and me,
which one do you think is yours?</font>

268
00:12:57,701 --> 00:12:59,873
<font color="#FFFFFF">No!</font>

269
00:13:02,831 --> 00:13:05,251
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know where the tower is.</font>

270
00:13:24,604 --> 00:13:27,701
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sky Spiders have flown you
as far as their complex religion allows.</font>

271
00:13:27,856 --> 00:13:30,705
<font color="#FFFFFF">They set you down and express,
through intricate prancing...</font>

272
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:33,115
<font color="#FFFFFF">- ... directions to the tower.
- Yes.</font>

273
00:13:35,155 --> 00:13:36,959
<font color="#FFFFFF">Father, forgive me.</font>

274
00:13:37,115 --> 00:13:39,335
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have travelled so far from you.</font>

275
00:13:39,494 --> 00:13:42,792
<font color="#FFFFFF">How many game days
since the Skull River ripped us apart?</font>

276
00:13:42,956 --> 00:13:45,802
<font color="#FFFFFF">How many real hours
since I've gone pee?</font>

277
00:13:45,959 --> 00:13:47,299
<font color="#FFFFFF">We seek this necromancer.</font>

278
00:13:48,669 --> 00:13:50,057
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why? Why?</font>

279
00:13:50,212 --> 00:13:53,677
<font color="#FFFFFF">Our reasons are dreams,
our dreams, dust.</font>

280
00:13:53,966 --> 00:13:57,514
<font color="#FFFFFF">I send word on wings of sparrows...</font>

281
00:13:58,263 --> 00:14:00,980
<font color="#FFFFFF">in hopes they might find you.</font>

282
00:14:01,307 --> 00:14:04,818
<font color="#FFFFFF">Abed says the odds
are near impossible.</font>

283
00:14:05,102 --> 00:14:07,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's enough for me.</font>

284
00:14:09,524 --> 00:14:13,154
<font color="#FFFFFF">Should you receive this message,
I know of a way to reunite.</font>

285
00:14:13,318 --> 00:14:14,956
<font color="#FFFFFF">According to my character sheet...</font>

286
00:14:15,113 --> 00:14:18,494
<font color="#FFFFFF">if I rub the blade of our magic
family sword while you rub the hilt...</font>

287
00:14:18,658 --> 00:14:22,418
<font color="#FFFFFF">twin beacons of light
will reveal our locations to each other.</font>

288
00:14:22,578 --> 00:14:25,758
<font color="#FFFFFF">Each night,
I will think of you and rub...</font>

289
00:14:26,039 --> 00:14:30,761
<font color="#FFFFFF">praying for the night
fate will find us rubbing together.</font>

290
00:14:30,919 --> 00:14:35,926
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your son, Joseph Gordon Diehard.</font>

291
00:14:42,682 --> 00:14:44,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">Something strange has happened.</font>

292
00:14:44,558 --> 00:14:46,943
<font color="#FFFFFF">A sparrow lands
on Riggs Diehard's shoulder.</font>

293
00:14:47,352 --> 00:14:48,480
<font color="#FFFFFF">It carries a note.</font>

294
00:14:57,238 --> 00:15:00,750
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Abed, I rub my sword's hilt"?</font>

295
00:15:00,908 --> 00:15:02,995
<font color="#FFFFFF">Beam of light shoots up
from your location...</font>

296
00:15:03,160 --> 00:15:05,047
<font color="#FFFFFF">as the hilt of Diehard
seeks its blade.</font>

297
00:15:05,205 --> 00:15:08,751
<font color="#FFFFFF">The beam arcs and meets an equal
beam in the woods to the north.</font>

298
00:15:08,917 --> 00:15:10,303
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that where the others are?</font>

299
00:15:10,460 --> 00:15:12,630
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes, 10 miles away, same as you.</font>

300
00:15:12,794 --> 00:15:14,716
<font color="#FFFFFF">So we'll be arriving at the tower...</font>

301
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,552
<font color="#FFFFFF">At the same time tomorrow morning.</font>

302
00:15:16,716 --> 00:15:18,389
<font color="#FFFFFF">This began as a race.</font>

303
00:15:18,551 --> 00:15:21,019
<font color="#FFFFFF">But it may end in war.</font>

304
00:15:21,386 --> 00:15:22,811
<font color="#FFFFFF">Does anybody have a toothpick?</font>

305
00:15:22,971 --> 00:15:25,356
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got a piece of popcorn
stuck in my tooth.</font>

306
00:15:25,517 --> 00:15:28,565
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like, right under the gum.
I've been trying like for 15 minutes...</font>

307
00:15:28,727 --> 00:15:32,073
<font color="#FFFFFF">with, you know, my tooth
and then with my tongue and my finger.</font>

308
00:15:32,231 --> 00:15:34,817
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm always one tooth off,
and I just can't seem to...</font>

309
00:15:34,984 --> 00:15:37,286
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, hello, there we go. Anyway...</font>

310
00:15:37,445 --> 00:15:40,209
<font color="#FFFFFF">But it may end in war.</font>

311
00:15:49,499 --> 00:15:51,504
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maybe after all we've been through...</font>

312
00:15:51,668 --> 00:15:53,886
<font color="#FFFFFF">we should just call this thing off.</font>

313
00:15:54,044 --> 00:15:55,931
<font color="#FFFFFF">What, you think that's up to us?</font>

314
00:15:56,088 --> 00:15:59,600
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've seen the way he talks to me,
doesn't want his father in his life.</font>

315
00:15:59,759 --> 00:16:02,606
<font color="#FFFFFF">He'll do anything to win,
and that includes attacking you.</font>

316
00:16:02,761 --> 00:16:05,525
<font color="#FFFFFF">And you best believe
that your little friends in there...</font>

317
00:16:05,682 --> 00:16:07,272
<font color="#FFFFFF">are drinking up his Kool-Aid.</font>

318
00:16:07,432 --> 00:16:10,696
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is a man who thinks
of grandchildren like trophies.</font>

319
00:16:13,105 --> 00:16:15,407
<font color="#FFFFFF">Which is why he'll play to win.</font>

320
00:16:15,817 --> 00:16:17,453
<font color="#FFFFFF">And why I can't let him.</font>

321
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:25,875
<font color="#FFFFFF">Rise, brave, sweet Dingleberry.</font>

322
00:16:26,034 --> 00:16:27,588
<font color="#FFFFFF">Rise.</font>

323
00:16:27,745 --> 00:16:30,296
<font color="#FFFFFF">Both parties have arrived
at the black tower.</font>

324
00:16:32,417 --> 00:16:33,461
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hi, guys.</font>

325
00:16:33,625 --> 00:16:35,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Father.
- Joseph Gordon.</font>

326
00:16:37,797 --> 00:16:41,178
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are here so Tristram Steelheart,
Lord of the Sky Spiders...</font>

327
00:16:41,341 --> 00:16:44,605
<font color="#FFFFFF">can slay the necromancer. You cool
or are we gonna have to get red?</font>

328
00:16:44,761 --> 00:16:47,976
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tiny Nuggins, Waterboarder of Goblins,
will do the slaying...</font>

329
00:16:48,140 --> 00:16:51,438
<font color="#FFFFFF">because every man has the right
to hang out with his grandson.</font>

330
00:16:51,602 --> 00:16:52,895
<font color="#FFFFFF">Too bad you're outnumbered.</font>

331
00:16:53,062 --> 00:16:54,568
<font color="#FFFFFF">No, they're not.</font>

332
00:16:54,938 --> 00:16:56,778
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not part of this.</font>

333
00:16:56,941 --> 00:16:58,697
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am Joseph Gordon Diehard...</font>

334
00:16:58,860 --> 00:17:01,908
<font color="#FFFFFF">and I am only here to hug my father,
which I now do.</font>

335
00:17:02,071 --> 00:17:03,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a trick!</font>

336
00:17:03,322 --> 00:17:05,742
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm not letting him hug me.
- I hug my father!</font>

337
00:17:05,909 --> 00:17:08,673
<font color="#FFFFFF">- He has gunpowder in his pants.
- I draw my sword. Stay back!</font>

338
00:17:08,827 --> 00:17:10,335
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I draw an arrow.
- So do I!</font>

339
00:17:10,497 --> 00:17:12,002
<font color="#FFFFFF">Troll sound!</font>

340
00:17:12,164 --> 00:17:13,338
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Lower your sword?
- No!</font>

341
00:17:13,500 --> 00:17:16,002
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Dean, are you...?
- I hug my father!</font>

342
00:17:16,169 --> 00:17:17,759
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're impaled.</font>

343
00:17:31,934 --> 00:17:33,322
<font color="#FFFFFF">Worth it.</font>

344
00:17:33,478 --> 00:17:34,865
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good Lord.</font>

345
00:17:35,020 --> 00:17:36,278
<font color="#FFFFFF">Son slayer!</font>

346
00:17:36,439 --> 00:17:38,028
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I attack Jeff!
- Arrow at Chang!</font>

347
00:17:38,191 --> 00:17:40,362
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Arrow at Annie!
- I head for the door.</font>

348
00:17:40,527 --> 00:17:42,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">So do I!</font>

349
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:44,039
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Taste the blade of Diehard!
- I run!</font>

350
00:17:44,197 --> 00:17:45,952
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Turn a snake into a rope!
- Two arrows!</font>

351
00:17:46,115 --> 00:17:48,001
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Spear, spear!
- I take the kid, pop him.</font>

352
00:17:48,159 --> 00:17:51,337
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Three damage.
- Lightning bolt, lightning bolt!</font>

353
00:17:51,496 --> 00:17:53,714
<font color="#FFFFFF">Heal our moderate wounds!</font>

354
00:17:53,873 --> 00:17:57,799
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I spray all over them.
- I hold Britta's face in a puddle.</font>

355
00:17:57,961 --> 00:17:59,882
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Seven damage.
- Cleave, cleave, cleave!</font>

356
00:18:00,255 --> 00:18:04,134
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I fire two arrows.
- I drink from the Chalice of Knowing.</font>

357
00:18:04,299 --> 00:18:07,348
<font color="#FFFFFF">Dingleberry smash!</font>

358
00:18:07,511 --> 00:18:11,902
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Plus three, demonic eye look.
- Pull and shove it up them!</font>

359
00:18:12,057 --> 00:18:14,193
<font color="#FFFFFF">After that,
I put one right behind the ear.</font>

360
00:18:14,352 --> 00:18:16,238
<font color="#FFFFFF">I fire two...</font>

361
00:18:17,230 --> 00:18:18,902
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sir Riggs, hand in character sheet.</font>

362
00:18:28,991 --> 00:18:30,913
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Top floor, one door.
- I open it.</font>

363
00:18:31,076 --> 00:18:32,713
<font color="#FFFFFF">- "Flame Strike."
- You did already.</font>

364
00:18:32,871 --> 00:18:34,045
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Mace!
- Okay. Missed.</font>

365
00:18:34,204 --> 00:18:36,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hit him with a throwing dagger.
- Used all your knives.</font>

366
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:39,219
<font color="#FFFFFF">What?
Will one of you guys take care...?</font>

367
00:18:39,376 --> 00:18:41,845
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What? You're all dead? I keep going.
- I follow.</font>

368
00:18:42,005 --> 00:18:43,925
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've reached
the necromancer's workshop.</font>

369
00:18:44,089 --> 00:18:46,938
<font color="#FFFFFF">You see his bed, bottles of goop,
some necromancing crap...</font>

370
00:18:47,093 --> 00:18:48,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">but no necromancer.</font>

371
00:18:48,595 --> 00:18:51,394
<font color="#FFFFFF">I search. Can I search
or are you gonna stab me in the back?</font>

372
00:18:51,556 --> 00:18:54,058
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, I am a thief, not a wuss.
