373
00:18:55,226 --> 00:18:57,444
<font color="#FFFFFF">You find a secret door.
It's easy, already open.</font>

374
00:18:57,604 --> 00:19:00,865
<font color="#FFFFFF">It leads to a ladder which goes
straight down to another open door...</font>

375
00:19:01,023 --> 00:19:03,788
<font color="#FFFFFF">- ... on the back of the tower.
- Man. Way to go.</font>

376
00:19:03,942 --> 00:19:05,532
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's great. He just got away.</font>

377
00:19:05,694 --> 00:19:08,375
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, you can't just say he's gone.
You owe us an ending.</font>

378
00:19:09,656 --> 00:19:11,163
<font color="#FFFFFF">I owe you nothing.</font>

379
00:19:11,326 --> 00:19:12,832
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am a Dungeon Master.</font>

380
00:19:12,993 --> 00:19:15,711
<font color="#FFFFFF">I create a boundless world,
and I bind it by rules.</font>

381
00:19:15,872 --> 00:19:17,876
<font color="#FFFFFF">Too heavy for a bridge? It breaks.</font>

382
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:21,137
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get hit? Take damage. Spend an hour
outside someone's front door...</font>

383
00:19:21,294 --> 00:19:24,557
<font color="#FFFFFF">fighting over who gets to kill him?
He leaves through the back.</font>

384
00:19:24,713 --> 00:19:27,810
<font color="#FFFFFF">He's out there. You might find him,
if you get your crap together.</font>

385
00:19:27,967 --> 00:19:30,304
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey, guys.
Take it from a bunch of ghosts.</font>

386
00:19:30,470 --> 00:19:32,022
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is no kind of life.</font>

387
00:19:32,180 --> 00:19:34,433
<font color="#FFFFFF">You need fresh air and frozen yogurt.</font>

388
00:19:34,598 --> 00:19:36,817
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's on me. Hug it out.</font>

389
00:19:36,976 --> 00:19:38,816
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Gag me.
- Who even uses that phrase?</font>

390
00:19:38,978 --> 00:19:40,484
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm climbing down the ladder.</font>

391
00:19:40,646 --> 00:19:43,445
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm gonna find this guy.
- I stay and search the workshop.</font>

392
00:19:43,607 --> 00:19:46,325
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Any stuff there that can heal me?
- Some potions.</font>

393
00:19:46,486 --> 00:19:47,992
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, well, I get half of that.</font>

394
00:19:48,153 --> 00:19:49,661
<font color="#FFFFFF">You just went down the ladder.</font>

395
00:19:49,823 --> 00:19:51,827
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can...
Can I hear him looting upstairs?</font>

396
00:19:51,990 --> 00:19:53,498
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not if I move about silently.</font>

397
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:57,087
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine, fine. If I heal you,
can we divide the potions?</font>

398
00:19:57,247 --> 00:19:59,833
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, but I decide who gets what.</font>

399
00:19:59,999 --> 00:20:01,838
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine, but we've gotta be wary of traps.</font>

400
00:20:02,000 --> 00:20:03,294
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Wand of Orcus.
- I don't...</font>

401
00:20:03,461 --> 00:20:04,634
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's going on?</font>

402
00:20:04,796 --> 00:20:09,305
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Give me a... I'm up to here with you.
- Want to get the necromancer or not?</font>

403
00:20:09,467 --> 00:20:11,188
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do they like each other now?</font>

404
00:20:11,344 --> 00:20:14,441
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you kidding me? They can't stand
being in the same room.</font>

405
00:20:14,596 --> 00:20:16,981
<font color="#FFFFFF">I also don't think
they can handle being apart.</font>

406
00:20:17,142 --> 00:20:23,357
<font color="#FFFFFF">And I think they just found a way
to avoid doing either.</font>

407
00:20:26,776 --> 00:20:30,038
<font color="#FFFFFF">And that's the best
most fathers and sons can do.</font>

408
00:20:31,114 --> 00:20:32,621
<font color="#FFFFFF">You've made me so proud today.</font>

409
00:20:34,366 --> 00:20:38,247
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Know where we can buy a real sword?
- Oh, Jeffrey.</font>

410
00:20:45,377 --> 00:20:48,675
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're still at the entrance
to the Chamber of Grief.</font>

411
00:20:50,884 --> 00:20:52,556
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your move, Mr. Tickles.</font>

412
00:20:55,721 --> 00:20:59,398
<font color="#FFFFFF">You successfully pour more tea
into Count Frogula's cup.</font>

413
00:20:59,558 --> 00:21:02,406
<font color="#FFFFFF">That puts it at Hillary Rodham Kitten.</font>

414
00:21:02,561 --> 00:21:06,571
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay, you attempt to pass crumpets.</font>

415
00:21:08,609 --> 00:21:09,866
<font color="#FFFFFF">You fail.</font>

416
00:21:10,028 --> 00:21:13,788
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm getting frustrated. If you take a look
at your inventories, you'll see...</font>

417
00:21:13,948 --> 00:21:15,372
<font color="#FFFFFF">Abed, are you almost done?</font>

418
00:21:15,532 --> 00:21:17,205
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't sleep without my stuffies.</font>

419
00:21:17,367 --> 00:21:19,171
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fine. Hold on.</font>

420
00:21:20,246 --> 00:21:23,010
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh, a goblin notices you
and murders you all. You're dead.</font>

421
00:21:23,165 --> 00:21:24,720
<font color="#FFFFFF">They're all yours.</font>

